</ol>
<p>The above are only the stem forms of the verbs; to these one must add various verb endings in order to get the fully conjugated verb. The following table lists the most common conjugations. See <a href="/wiki/Japanese_verb_conjugations" title="Japanese verb conjugations" class="mw-redirect">Japanese verb conjugations</a> for a full list. In cases where the form is different based on the conjugation group of the verb, arrows point to the correct formation rule.</p>
